Email retrieval mode
Email r-r-retriefal mode

The mail retrieval mode can be set to standard (for dedicated Internet connections), ETRN (recommended for dialup connections), or multi-drop (for dialup connections if ETRN is not supported by your Internet provider).
Ze mail r-r-retriefal mode kan be set to standard (for dedicated Internet konnections), ETR-r-rN (recommended for dialup konnections), or multi-drop (for dialup konnections if ETR-r-rN ist not supported by your Internet profider).

Delegate mail server
Delegate mail serfer

Your e-smith system includes a complete, full-featured email server. However, if for some reason you wish to delegate email processing to another system, specify the IP address of the delegate system here. For normal operation, leave this field blank.
Your e-smid system includes a komplete, full-featured email serfer. Howefer, if for some r-r-reason you visch to delegate email processingkt to anoder system, specify ze IP address uff de delegate system here. For normal operation, leafe dis field blank.

