Secondary mail server
Secondary mail serfer

As you are using ETRN or Multi-drop, you must specify the hostname or IP address of your secondary mail server.
As you are usingkt ETR-r-rN or Multi-drop, you must specify ze hostname or IP address uff your secondary mail serfer.

During office hours (8:00am to 6:00pm on weekdays)
Duringkt office hours (8:00am to 6:00pm on veekdays)

You can control how frequently the e-smith server and gateway contacts your secondary email server to fetch email. More frequent connections mean that you receive your email more quickly, but also cause Internet requests to be sent more often, possibly increasing your phone and Internet charges.
You kan kontrol how frequently ze e-smid serfer undt gateway kontacts your secondary email serfer to fetch email. More frequent konnections mean dat you r-r-receife your email more quickly, but also kause Internet r-r-requests to be sent more often, possibly increasingkt your phone undt Internet kharges.

